6. Real-Time Data Integration (Nice-to-Have)

Labor Market Data Integration: Real-time labor market data is crucial for providing up-to-date insights on emerging skill demands. APIs or partnerships with labor data providers will be required to keep the system current.
Dynamic Skill Network Updates: The skill network will need to be updated regularly to reflect these changes. A real-time data pipeline using technologies like Apache Kafka or AWS Lambda may be necessary for this.
